OL,7,FAlmost a fifth of people were deemed
OL,8,Fat risk of poverty at least once
OL,9,Fbetween 2015 and 2023, according to a
OL,10,Fstudy.
OL,12,FThe Economic and Social Research
OL,13,FInstitute (ESRI) published research
OL,14,Fexamining the complexities of income
OL,15,Fpoverty and deprivation and how they
OL,16,Fintertwine.
