OL,7,FIt said the stronger effect for the
OL,8,Folder population could be explained by
OL,9,Fthe fact that the State pension was
OL,10,Ffrozen in cash terms in 2020 and 2021.
OL,12,FThe ESRI report, published in
OL,13,Fpartnership with the Department of
OL,14,FSocial Protection, used longitudinal
OL,15,Fdata from the Survey on Income and
OL,16,FLiving Conditions (SILC) ` the study
OL,17,Fexplores the dynamics of poverty.
