OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe report said that implementing
OL,8,F"targeted" policy measures to support
OL,9,Flone parents, large families, and
OL,10,Fhouseholds with a person with
OL,11,Fdisabilities is essential to help
OL,12,Fthose at high risk of poverty.
OL,14,FIt said timely adjustments to social
OL,15,Fwelfare payments, including pensions,
OL,16,Fwould be "critical" to protect
OL,17,Fvulnerable groups from inflation.
