OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FCo-author Anousheh Alamir said the
OL,8,Freport highlighted "the complex nature
OL,9,Fof poverty" and how different groups
OL,10,Fface different risks over various time
OL,11,Fperiods.
OL,13,F"Over two year stretches, lone parent
OL,14,Ffamilies and households with a
OL,15,Fdisabled adult are found to be the
OL,16,Fmost at risk of income poverty and/or
OL,17,Fmaterial deprivation for one year only.
