OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,F"And while they are also the most
OL,8,Flikely to be materially deprived two
OL,9,Fyears in a row (i.e persistently),
OL,10,Flarge families are the most at risk of
OL,11,Fincome poverty during that time.
OL,13,F"Thus, different groups are vulnerable
OL,14,Fto different forms and durations of
OL,15,Fpoverty, an insight that should be key
OL,16,Ffor effective policy."
